# Hermes — track only config.yaml and SOUL.md under .hermes/.
# Everything else under .hermes/ is secrets, local state, or personal data.
.hermes/*
!.hermes/config.yaml
!.hermes/SOUL.md

# Belt-and-suspenders: never commit Hermes secrets/state even if force-added.
**/.env
**/auth.json
**/auth.lock
**/state.db
**/state.db-*
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal
.hermes/memories/
.hermes/sessions/
.hermes/logs/
.hermes/cache/
.hermes/mnemosyne/
.hermes/plugins/
